   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,294:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Requests (
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,294:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: requests
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,294:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: )
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,295:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : Overcomes vanilla 
