   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,303:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : The dominant library for screen-scraping. BS4 allowed us to parse the
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,303:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: complex, nested tag trees (
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,304:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: <article>
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,305:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: , 
