   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,306:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ) dynamically,
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,307:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: avoiding brittle Regex searches against raw HTML.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,308:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 3.3. Data Manipulation 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,308:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: &
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,309:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Storage
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,309:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,310:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Pandas
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,311:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : Crucial for reshaping our scraped dictionaries into a highly optimized, column-oriented 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,311:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: DataFrame
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,313:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: . Pandas enables vectorized operations ensuring that cleaning thousands of rows occurs
