   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,318:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: operated on using underlying C/C++ compilation for extreme speeds.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,319:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 3.4. The Machine Learning Engine
