   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,321:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: sklearn
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,321:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: )
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,322:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : Used to construct our rigorous AI pipeline. Specifically leveraging 
