   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,331:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: .
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,335:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The deterministic nature of Scikit-Learn makes it vastly superior to massive Deep Learning
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,336:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: frameworks (like PyTorch) for tabular, structured datasets of this size.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,337:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 3.5. Presentation 
