   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,356:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: )
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,357:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: This module is isolated to ensure single-responsibility formatting. It houses the critical data engineering functions:
