   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,362:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,363:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Applies conditional scalar multiplication. E.g., if the capturing group matches 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,363:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: crore
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,366:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: , it multiplies the float value by 10,000,000. It effectively standardizes all
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,367:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: price metrics to a base integer of 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,367:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: PKR
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,368:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: .
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,368:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  2 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,369:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: parse_area_to_marla(area_str)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,369:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: :
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,370:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,370:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Parses the chaotic sizing system used in Pakistani real estate.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,371:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,372:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Normalizes completely differing metrics natively to 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,372:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Marla
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,373:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: . It converts Kanals
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,373:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: (Kanal 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,373:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: *
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,374:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  20), Square Yards (Sq Yd / 30.25), and Square Feet (Sq Ft / 225.0) strictly
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,375:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: accurately.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,375:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  3 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,376:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: fetch_live_listings(num_pages)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,376:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: :
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,377:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,377:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Loops iteratively constructing URL payloads: 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,378:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: f'https://www.zameen.com/Plots/Quetta-18-{page}.html'
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,379:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: .
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,379:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,379:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Traps requests in 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,380:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: try/except
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,382:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  blocks to prevent network outages on individual
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,383:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: pages from crashing the entire scrape.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,383:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,384:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Synthesizes findings and packages them via 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,384:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: pd.DataFrame()
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,385:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: .
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,385:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: B. The User Interface 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,386:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: &
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,387:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  AI Module (
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,387:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: app.py
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,388:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: )
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,388:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: This serves as both the view layer and the machine learning executor.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,389:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  1 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,389:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: fetch_and_train()
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,390:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Function
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,390:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: :
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,391:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,392:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Interlocks UI state arrays. Triggers the scraper and awaits the DataFrame payload.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,392:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,393:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The Pipeline
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,393:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : We define a 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,394:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Pipeline
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,394:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  connecting two crucial components:
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,395:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,396:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Preprocessing (
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,396:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: OneHotEncoder
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,397:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: )
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,398:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : Since mathematical models
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,399:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: cannot understand string text like 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,400:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,400:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: DHA Defence
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,401:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,405:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: , this encoder
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,409:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: converts every distinct location into its own binary column (0 or 1).
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,410:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: E.g., The dataset suddenly balloons to 30 columns where 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,410:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Is_DHA_Defence = 1
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,411:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  while all others are 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,412:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 0
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,412:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: .
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,413:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,413:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Regression (
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,414:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: RandomForestRegressor(n_estimators=100)
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,415:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: )
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,431:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: : Our
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,447:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: core model. Rather than fitting a single straight line (Linear
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,457:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Regression), Random Forest generates 100 deep decision trees based
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,466:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: on randomized subsets of the data. One tree might heavily favor
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,468:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Size, while another severely penalizes a specific location. By forcing
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,469:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: all 100 trees to 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,470:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,470:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: vote
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,471:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,477:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  on the final price and averaging their outcome,
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,481:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: the model massively mitigates prediction variance and naturally
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,483:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ignores extreme outlier listings (like a heavily overpriced fake
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,483:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: listing on Zameen).
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,484:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  2 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,484:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Session State Memory Cache (
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,485:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: st.session_state
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,486:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: )
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,486:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: :
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,487:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,489:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Web applications are naturally stateless; they forget everything every time you click
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,490:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: a button. By storing 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,491:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: st.session_state.df
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,491:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  and 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,492:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: st.session_state.model
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,493:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: , the gigabyte-scale RAM allocation of the
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,494:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Scikit-Learn tree object is preserved.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,495:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  3 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,495:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Responsive UI Engine
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,496:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: :
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,497:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,498:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Organizes data utilizing column-based grids formatting via 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,498:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: st.columns()
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,501:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: . It
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,502:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: dynamically presents a live-updating table of the raw dataset so the user can
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,503:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: cross-verify the AI
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,503:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,504:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s calculation against current realities. Let
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,504:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,505:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s say the AI outputs 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,505:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,505:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 21
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,506:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Lakh
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,507:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,512:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: . A user can physically look sideways to the table and observe that recent 5
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,514:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Marla plots in that location were listed at 20.5 Lakh and 22 Lakh respectively,
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,514:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: proving algorithmic integrity.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,515:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 5. Summary 
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,516:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: &
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,516:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Future Scope
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,528:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The Quetta Live Real Estate Price Estimator flawlessly showcases how bridging the gap between Data Engineering
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,531:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: (Web Scraping) and Data Science (Machine Learning) creates profoundly impactful software. By refusing to
