   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,540:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: historical timelines to measure local real-estate inflation percentages mathematically.
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,541:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: l
   DEBUG: 2026-04-12 21:59:32,541:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Incorporating additional features currently ignored, such as 
